### Data Pipeline
```
User CSV upload → DataHarvester (clean/profile) → TrendAnalyst (ReAct EDA + Google Trends)
  → Forecaster (Prophet + FFT) → MCTS Optimizer (inventory sim) → OrderManager (LLM text)
  → Notifier (Discord webhook)
