## Step 7 — Top 10 Red Flags

1. **🚩 Paper admits results are fabricated (Line 452):** *"The following results represent plausible benchmark values... will be replaced with actual experimental results."* This note exists **inside the submitted paper**, making every quantitative claim unverifiable and the paper unpublishable.

2. **🚩 Hardcoded Bullwhip "before" value:** `bullwhip_before = 2.4` is a literal constant at line 520 of [mcts_optimizer.py](file:///c:/Users/Dorem/Desktop/web-dev/AURAChain/aura_chain/app/agents/mcts_optimizer.py). The "improvement" is computed against this fiction, not measured data.

3. **🚩 No baselines implemented:** The paper claims comparison against ARIMA(1,1,1), ROP, (s,S), and single-agent LLM. **None of these exist in the codebase.** The only "baseline" is "no reordering" — trivially beaten.

4. **🚩 In-sample MAPE evaluation:** The forecaster evaluates MAPE on training data ([forecaster.py](file:///c:/Users/Dorem/Desktop/web-dev/AURAChain/aura_chain/test_forecaster.py) L379-386), not out-of-sample holdout. This produces artificially favorable numbers.

5. **🚩 Fictional ablation study:** Tables 6-7 in the paper report component-by-component ablation results. There is no code to selectively disable components and measure impact. These numbers were invented.

6. **🚩 OpenTelemetry/Grafana claims are false:** README and paper claim "Full Observability: OpenTelemetry + Prometheus/Grafana instrumentation." The [observability.py](file:///c:/Users/Dorem/Desktop/web-dev/AURAChain/aura_chain/app/core/observability.py) module is a custom logger class. No OTel SDK, no Prometheus exporter, no Grafana dashboards exist.

7. **🚩 "Multi-model" claim is misleading:** All agents use `groq_client`. The paper claims native integration with "Anthropic Claude, Google Gemini, and OpenAI GPT-4o" as if these are direct API integrations. In reality, Groq is the single API provider.

8. **🚩 Order Manager is a trivial LLM wrapper (75 LOC):** The paper describes "automated purchase order drafting" and "approval workflows." The code is a single LLM prompt that returns free-text. No structured PO, no vendor database, no approval flow.

9. **🚩 Synthetic dataset evaluates the system:** Evaluating your system on a dataset you designed for it is circular. The 50k MSME synthetic dataset should be a stress-test supplement, not the primary evaluation dataset.

10. **🚩 No email notification despite claims:** The paper claims "Email and Discord alert dispatch" for the Notifier agent. The code implements Discord-only.

